Template: jira/username
Type: string
Default: jira
Description: Dedicated system account for the jira:
 JIRA runs within a tomcat server and must use a dedicated account for 
 its operation so that the system's security is not compromised by running it 
 with superuser privileges.

Template: jira/groupname
Type: string
Default: jira
Description: Dedicated system group for jira:
 JIRA runs within tomcat server and must use a dedicated group for its 
 operation so that the system's security is not compromised by running it with 
 superuser privileges.
